gurU dI ikrpw nwl mYN auhI kMm krW (ijn@W krky mYnUM prmwqmw dw nwm pRwpq hovy),
qy prmwqmw dy nwm-rMg ivc rMigAw hoieAw mYN prmwqmw dw gux gWdw rhW ]5]
gurU dI d`sI hoeI syvw dI rwhIN ijs mnu`K ny Awpxw AMdrlw Awqmk jIvn pCwx ilAw,
aus dy mn ivc Awqmk jIvn dyx vwlw Awqmk AwnMd dyx vwlw hrI-nwm v`s ipAw (smJo)[
auh mnu`K pRBU dI is&q-swlwh dI bwxI dI rwhIN hr roz nwm-rMg ivc rMigAw rihMdw hY ]6]
(pr ieh Kyf jIv dy v`s dI nhIN) jdoN ipAwrw pRBU iksy jIv nUM Awpxy nwm ivc lgWdw hY qdoN hI koeI l`gdw hY,
qdoN hI gur-Sbd dI rwhIN auh haumY nUM mwr ky (ies vloN sdw) sucyq rihMdw hY[
iPr lok prlok ivc sdw Awqmk AwnMd aus dy swhmxy mOjUd rihMdw hY ]7]
pr cMcl mn (haumY nUM mwrn dw) qrIkw nhIN jwx skdw,
ikauNik mnmuiK dw mn (ivkwrW nwl sdw) mYlw rihMdw hY, auh gurU dy Sbd nwl sWJ nhIN pw skdw[
gurU dy d`sy rwh qy qurn vwlw mnu`K prmwqmw dw nwm ismrdw hY qy pivqR jIvn vwlw huMdw hY ]8]
mYN pRBU jI A`gy ieh Ardwis krdw hW ik,
gurmuKW dI sMgq ivc myrw invws bixAw rhy,
qy myry AMdr prmwqmw dw nwm cmk pey, qy auh nwm myry pwp klyS k`t dyvy ]9]
ijhVw gurU dI bwxI nUM ivcwr ky cMgw Awcrn bxwxw smJ lYNdw hY,
qy gurU dy bcnW auqy qur ky iek prmwqmw nwl sWJ pWdw hY,
aus dw mn prmwqmw dy nwm-rMg ivc rMigAw rihMdw hY[ hy nwnk! ]10]7]
rwg Awsw iv`c gurU nwnkdyv jI dI bwxI[
gur-Sbd qoN KuMJ ky (mwieAw-vyVRihAw) mn pwgl hwQI (smwn) hY,
qy mwieAw dy moh dy kwrn (sMswr-) jMgl ivc Btkdw iPrdw hY[
(mwieAw dy moh dy kwrn) ijn@W nUM Awqmk mOq dbw lYNdI hY auh ieDr auDr Btkdy iPrdy hn[
jo mnu`K gurU dy snmuK huMdw hY auh Bwl ky Awpxy AMdr prmwqmw dw itkwxw l`B lYNdw hY (qy Btkxw ivc nhIN pYNdw) ]1]
gurU dy Sbd (ivc juVn) qoN ibnw mn iek QW itikAw nhIN rih skdw[
(ies mn nUM itkwx vwsqy gur-Sbd dI rwhIN) prmwqmw dw nwm ismro jo bhuq hI pivqR hY, Aqy hor rs C`fo jo kOVy BI hn qy haumY nUM vDWdy hn ]1] rhwau]
(mwieAw dy moh ivc hYrwn hoieAw) ieh mn AwpxI sUJ gvw lYNdw hY, iPr d`so, ieh BtkxoN ikvyN rih skdw hY?
Awpxy Asly dI sUJ qo ibnw ieh mn Awqmk mOq dw du`K shwrygw hI[
ijs mnu`K auqy prmwqmw Awp b^SS krdw hY, aus nUM gurU iml pYNdw hY,
auh duKdweI Awqmk mOq nUM shwr lYNdw hY, sdw-iQr pRBU (aus nUM Awqmk jIvn vl) pRyrdw hY ]2]
(mwieAw dy moh ivc hYrwn hoieAw) ieh mn hor hor Dwrimk rsmW rIvwj krdw iPrdw hY,
qy ieh mn pMjW q`qW qoN jMimAw hoieAw hY (Bwv, jnm mrn dy gyV ivc leI iPrdw hY)[
mwieAw-vyVRihAw ieh mn lwlcI bx jWdw hY, mUrK ho jWdw hY[
jyhVw mnu`K gurU dy snmuK ho ky pRBU dw nwm jpdw hY aus dw mn suMdr (GwVq vwlw bx jWdw) hY ]3]
gurU dy snmuK hoey mnu`K dw mn prmwqmw nUM (Awpxy AMdr) QW dyNdw hY,
aus nUM aus pRBU dI sUJ ho jWdI hY jo iqMnW BvnW ivc ivAwpk hY[
(mwieAw dy moh ivc hYrwn hoieAw) ieh mn kdy jog-swDn krdw hY kdy mwieAw dy Bog Bogdw hY kdy qpW nwl srIr nUM kSt dyNdw hY (pr Awqmk AwnMd aus nUM ikqy nhIN l`Bdw)[
jyhVw mnu`K gurU dy snmuK huMdw hY auh hrI prmwqmw nUM Awpxy AMdr Koj lYNdw hY ]4]
(mwieAw dy moh ivc hYrwn hoieAw) ieh mn kdy (Awpxy vloN) haumY iqAwg ky (dunIAw C`f ky) vYrwgvwn bx jWdw hY,
kdy hryk srIr ivc (mwieAw-vyVHy mn nUM) mwiek Purnw qy duibDw Aw cMbVdy hn[
jyhVw mnu`K gurU dI srn pY ky rsW dw Gr nwm-rs c`Kdw hY,
aus nUM AMdr bwhr mhl dw mwlk-pRBU (id`sdw hY) jo (mwieAw dy moh qoN bcw ky) aus dI ie`zq r`Kdw hY ]5]
(mwieAw dy moh ivc hYrwn hoieAw) ieh mn kdy rx-BUmI ivc rwjw qy sUrmw bixAw ipAw hY[
pr jdoN ieh mn gurU dI srn pY ky pRBU dy nwm ivc juVdw hY qW (mwieAw dy h`ilAW vloN) infr ho jWdw hY,
kwmwidk pMjW (vYrIAW) nUM mwr dyNdw hY, Awpxy v`s ivc kr lYNdw hY,
haumY nUM mukw ky iehnW sBnW nUM ieko QW ivc (kwbU) kr lYNdw hY ]6]
gurU dy snmuK hoieAw ieh mn rwg (dRvYK) qy hor hor suAwd iqAwg dyNdw hY,
gurU dI srn pY ky ieh mn prmwqmw dI BgqI ivc juV ky (mwieAw dy h`ilAW vloN) sucyq ho jWdw hY[
jyhVw mnu`K gurU dy Sbd nUM Awpxy soc-mMfl ivc itkWdw hY, auh (AMdrly Awqmk KyVy dy) iek-rs (ho rhy gIq) nUM sux sux ky (aus ivc) ig`J jWdw hY,
Awpxy Awpy nUM Koj ky prmwqmw rUp ho jWdw hY ]7]
(jdoN) ieh mn (gurU dy snmuK huMdw hY qdoN) pivqR ho jWdw hY, ies nUM AMdr bwhr auh prmwqmw hI id`sdw hY[
gurU dy snmuK ho ky (ies mn dy AMdr) BgqI dI lgn l`g pYNdI hY, (ies dy AMdr pRBU dw) ipAwr (jwg pYNdw hY),
gurU dI ikRpw nwl ieh mn idn rwq prmwqmw dI is&q-swlwh krdw hY[
jo prmwqmw swrI isRStI dw mu`F hY jo prmwqmw jugW dy mu`F qoN mOjUd hY auh ies mn nUM hryk srIr ivc v`sdw id`s pYNdw hY ]8]
gurU dy snmuK ho ky ieh mn rsW dy Gr nwm-rs ivc msq ho jWdw hY,
gurU dy snmuK hoieAw ieh mn sB rsW dy somy pRBU nUM pCwx lYNdw hY[
jdoN gurU dy crnW ivc (ies mn dw) invws huMdw hY qW (ies dy AMdr prmwqmw dI) BgqI dw pRym (jwg pYNdw hY)[
hy nwnk! qdoN ieh mn gurmuKW dy dwsW dw dws bx jWdw hY ]9]8]
